================================================================================
Consolidation notes
================================================================================

The current `de-slop` skill combines these two sources into a single
deduplicated catalogue, with some content cut (factually-incorrect hyphenation
guidance, opinion/voice-injection guidance that fell outside the skill's
scope) and softening of rule framing where the upstream wording was overly
absolute. See the plugin's history for the consolidation rationale.
